  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n[IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker] --> Idle: File Opened (IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)\n\n    state \"User Edits File\" as UserAction\n    Idle --> UserAction: User types a character\n\n    state \"Request Lock\" as RequestLock {IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n        }\n    }\n\n    GrantLock --> LockedState: 200 OK\n    DenyLock --> ConflictState: 409 Conflict\n\n    state \"Locked (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\" as LockedState {IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream] --> Editing\n        Editing --> Heartbeat: Every 30s\n        Heartbeat --> ServerUpdate: UPDATE locks SET timestamp\n        ServerUpdate --> Editing: 200 OK\n        \n        Editing --> Unlock: User saves/closes/stops\n    }\n\n    state \"Conflict (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\" as ConflictState {IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController] --> ShowWarning: Display \"File Locked by User B\"\n        ShowWarning --> Idle: User cancels edit\n    }\n\n    Unlock --> Idle: DELETE /lock (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n    \n    note right of Heartbeat\n        Prevents \"Stale Locks\" if\n        PC crashes or loses power.\n    end note",
